Class Lambda

    public abstract class Lambda
extends java.lang.Object
implements Lazy, Applicable, Value

    This is the base class for all function values.

    Because all functions extend this, all functions are also Lazy values.

    Subclasses must implement Applicable.apply(java.lang.Object)
